About Gaza Rising

Gaza Rising is more than just a meme coin. It's a community-driven project that aims to raise awareness and support for humanitarian causes in Gaza. Inspired by the resilience of the people, we have combined meme culture with blockchain technology to create a symbol of hope and solidarity.

Roadmap

We have exciting plans for the future of Gaza Rising:

  • Phase 1 (Q3 2025): Token Creation & Launch
  • Phase 2 (Q3Q4 2025): Community Building & Charity Partnerships
  • Phase 3 (Q4 2025): NFT Collection Launch & Charity Fund
  • Phase 4 (2026): Decentralized Governance & DAO Implementation

Charity & Social Impact

A portion of the transaction fees will support humanitarian causes in Gaza. Our community will vote on which organizations to support, ensuring transparency and engagement.
